column5: Congrats Rob.  I too stopped after 2 children.  My kids are now 10, 9, and 5.  Hmmm.  THe irony is that I actually teach sex ed at school which of course includes contraception. lol!
Awesome I can't wait to read the fishing reports from you to. Hope mom is also doing great
Nice keeper:) congrats
LOL.. I did too Chris... the last one came out with the IUD in her hand!

Wow! this is awesome news... I knew she was going to pop soon based upon previous posts.... but this soon? wow man! this is kickbutt... I am happy for you and the misses... she has 10 toes and 10 fingers... good enough for any parent!  Congratulations,  G
Congrats to you and your family.
lol
Great news Rob, congrats to you and your wife.
Big congrats dood!  What a PB.
7.1 you say.  That would be around 20 inches then.  I can't believe you kept the 5 pounder and didn't cull it  Congrats pops  :clapping:
Congrats Rob
Congrats Rob. Keep wetting that line.

Thanks guys.  I would suggest that there is a distinction with a difference between a millionaires family and a million dollar family.     :rofl2:    Although I may find it less funny in a year or so.  Do as I say, not as I do, eh Chris. I'll keep it in mind.
Congrats!  Another future fishing partner!
Doesn't count...no OFC TOURNEY sign visible!  JK. CONGRATULATIONS ROB! A FULL STRINGER EH.   She's adorable.
Wow, congrats bud!!!
Congrats, a little bundle of joy for now lol, Tight Lines SBK
Congrats to you and your family Rob.
Cungrats bud. They're a lot of fun. Limit is 4 here in my 'zone'. Will limit out this August.
7 pounds 1 ounce    Big brother still doesn't get how his baby sister gets her dinner from under the blanket.  Now it's time for me to retire.
Congrats!  Retiring sucks lol
Awesome Rob    Congrats to the both of you
Fantastic Rob, congrats to everyone.  Having children is the best thing that can happen to folks.
Way to go!
WTG Rob !!!!!!!!!!!!!! Nice little keeper ya got there. She has good form for gripping a spinning combo too  So.......do i hear "Snip Snip" or is it just my ears playing tricks
Congrats to you and your wife, Rob. You might want to start looking at left handed baitcasters for her.
Congratulations.  She'll have you wrap around her little finger in no time. I know, 3 daughters and if it wasn't for the wife, they would have got away with murder.
Remember, you're allowed 5 on the lake.   :-).  Again, congrats.
Great news Rob. Congrats to the family.
Congrats KF

Congrats to you and the Mrs Rob!! You've got the "millionaire's family" now.. so get out there and buy a loto ticket!! LOL  Enjoy... nothing wrong with declaring the "factory closed", but I hope the punch press keeps running!
Perfect....someone to pass your red boots down to...lol....Congrates man!!!!!
Congrat's Rob, big news!
Congrats! Hope your son is old enough to go fishing, if not, your in for a tough season.
Congrats buddy!   :thumbsup_anim:    Another fishin' partner! Now go get snipped... it's a piece of cake and the buzz you get from the Valium is unreal! lol  Best wishes to mom and baby!
Congrats to both of you, Rob!!
Congrats to you and the family. Shes a cutie.
Congrats.
That Awesome Rob!!  Congrets to you and your family.
can't you do catch and release?
Congratulations on your million dollar family.   She is a keeper!
Congratulations .  May you and your family share a life of endless joy and love.
very cute...  now you have the mamas boy and the daddy's girl...  your a lucky guy..
Congrats!
